name: winbin
summary: Windows binaries for open-source C++ libraries
short_description:
Precompiled windows binaries for popular open-source C++ libraries. Compiled with recent versions of Microsoft Visual C++.

All libraries are compiled in both debug and release for both Win32 and x64. Some are compiled for static linking, whereas others for shared (DLL) linking.

Volunteers are welcome to assist in extending and updating the library database!
